      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), most of the <strong>chopped basil</strong> (save some for garnish!), <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>smashed</strong> <strong>avocado</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Squeeze in the juice of 1/4 of your<strong> lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>creamy avo pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
