    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine a squeeze of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon juice</strong> with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a large bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to the <strong>dressing</strong> and give it a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
