    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes are almost done, add your <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>to one half of the tray and return the tray to the oven for a further 2-3 min until toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch these like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
