    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti </strong>to the pot with the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>avo pesto</strong> and give it a good mix up until the spaghetti is fully coated in the pesto</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if it's looking a little dry!</p><p>Once everything is mixed together, add the<strong> roasted cherry tomatoes</strong> and stir them through gently – this is your <strong>creamy avo pesto spaghetti with roasted tomatoes</strong></p>",
